Created SETUP_GUIDE.md and added it to the zip. On another device:

Quick start:

Extract the zip
yarn install
Check firebase.config.ts has correct credentials
npx expo start --go → scan QR with Expo Go
Build APK:

npm install -g eas-cli
eas login
eas build --profile preview --platform android
Key things to check:

firebase.config.ts — Firebase API keys
google-services.json — Android Firebase config
app.json — package name, permissions
Node.js v18+ and Yarn installed
